    {
      "id": "styles-templates",
      "title": "üé® Styles and Templates",
      "type": "content",
      "subsections": [
        {
          "id": "understanding-styles",
          "title": "Understanding Styles",
          "type": "content",
          "markdown": "Styles are predefined formatting combinations applied to text for quick and consistent appearance.",
          "list": {
            "type": "bullet",
            "items": [
              "**Key Benefits:**",
              "Consistent formatting across documents",
              "Easy to update multiple elements at once",
              "Professional look with minimal effort"
            ]
          },
          "list": {
            "type": "bullet",
            "items": [
              "**Common Style Types:**",
              "**Heading Styles**: For document structure (Heading 1, 2, 3)",
              "**Paragraph Styles**: Control paragraph formatting",
              "**Character Styles**: Apply to selected text only",
              "**Linked Styles**: Apply to paragraphs or selected text"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "creating-custom-styles",
          "title": "‚úÖ Creating Custom Styles",
          "type": "list",
          "list": {
            "type": "numbered",
            "items": [
              "Format text as desired",
              "Select the formatted text",
              "Right-click ‚Üí **Styles ‚Üí Save Selection as a New Quick Style**",
              "Name your style and click **OK**"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "using-templates",
          "title": "Using Templates",
          "type": "content",
          "markdown": "Templates are pre-designed documents to save time.",
          "list": {
            "type": "bullet",
            "items": [
              "**Built-in Templates:**",
              "Letters",
              "Reports",
              "Resumes",
              "Newsletters",
              "Brochures"
            ]
          },
          "list": {
            "type": "numbered",
            "items": [
              "**Creating Custom Templates:**",
              "Design your document",
              "Go to **File ‚Üí Save As**",
              "Choose **Word Template (*.dotx)**",
              "Save in the Templates folder"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "headers-footers",
      "title": "üñã Headers, Footers, and Page Numbers",
      "type": "content",
      "subsections": [
        {
          "id": "adding-headers-footers",
          "title": "Adding Headers and Footers",
          "type": "content",
          "list": {
            "type": "numbered",
            "items": [
              "**Steps:**",
              "Go to **Insert ‚Üí Header** or **Insert ‚Üí Footer**",
              "Choose a built-in design or select **Edit Header/Footer**",
              "Type your content",
              "Double-click outside to exit"
            ]
          },
          "list": {
            "type": "bullet",
            "items": [
              "**Common Elements:**",
              "Document title",
              "Page numbers",
              "Date and time",
              "Company logo",
              "Author name"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "page-numbers",
          "title": "Page Numbers",
          "type": "content",
          "list": {
            "type": "numbered",
            "items": [
              "**Automatic Page Numbering:**",
              "Go to **Insert ‚Üí Page Number**",
              "Choose position (top, bottom, margins)",
              "Select a design style"
            ]
          },
          "list": {
            "type": "bullet",
            "items": [
              "**Custom Page Numbering:**",
              "Start from a specific number",
              "Use different formats (1, 2, 3 or A, B, C)",
              "Include chapter numbers"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "different-headers-footers",
          "title": "Different Headers/Footers",
          "type": "list",
          "list": {
            "type": "bullet",
            "items": [
              "**First Page Different**: Great for title pages",
              "**Odd & Even Pages**: Common in books/reports"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
